scopecontent.p:
The brochures and pamphlets in the "Information for Prospective Students" series underwent several title changes over the years. Holdings include:
Consider Michigan: Costs and Financial Aid: Information for Prospective Students (ca 1985 and 1988/89-1990/91);
Michigan can Help: A Guide to Financial Aid for Prospective Students and their Families (1991/92-1992/93);
Michigan Cares: A Guide to Financial Aid for Prospective Students and their Families (1993/94);
A Guide to Financial Aid for Prospective Students and their Families (1994/95);
University of Michigan Financial Aid: A Guide for Prospective Students and their Families (1995/96, September 1997, and September 1998); and Information for Prospective Students and their Families (ca 1996/97-1997/98).

Similarly, the brochures and pamphlets in the "Information for Prospective Students from Underrepresented Groups" series also have several titles. Also, earlier titles were split into separate brochures for Michigan residents and out-of-state students. Holdings include:
Consider Michigan: Non-Resident Costs and Financial Aid: Information for Prospective Students from Under-Represented Groups (ca 1985 and 1987/88-1988/89);
Consider Michigan: Michigan Resident Costs and Financial Aid: Information for Prospective Students from Under-Represented Groups (ca 1985 and 1987/88-1988/89);
Consider Michigan: Costs and Financial Aid: Information for Prospective Students from Under-Represented Groups (1989/90-1990/91);
Michigan can Help: A Guide to Financial Aid for Prospective Students from Under-represented Groups and their Families (1991/92);
Michigan can Help: A Guide to Financial Aid for Underrepresented Minority Groups (1992/93);
Michigan Cares: A Guide to Financial Aid for Underrepresented Minority Groups (1993/94);
A Guide to Financial Aid for Underrepresented Minority Groups (1994/95); and
University of Michigan Financial Aid: A Guide for Underrepresented Minority Students (1995/96).
